<Author>annie_se
<Content>Lovely hotel nearby shopping area We escaped to Berlin for a long weekend and stayed at Kurf眉rstendamm, which is nearby the shopping area (a lot of design clothes and shoes) with the same name. This hotel is also very close to the U-bahn (tube) Adenauerplatz and to the bus stop where you can take the local bus to/from the airport. The room was large and cleaned. The bathroom was decorated in light colours and was equipped with hairdryer. And the reception staffs were friendly. Their breakfast buffet offered a lot of options 鈥?different kind of freshly baked bread, hot and cold drinks, cold dishes (ham, smoked salmon, turkey and more), cereal etcetera. The only negative side was that they did not have a smoking room, so someone smoked in the corridor outside the rooms. This hotel is really inexpensive, for the price you pay you get a lot. Recommended! 
